{
  "name": "getTextAutoReply",
  "description": "Returns a single TextAutoReply instance for a given text auto reply id",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "id": {
        "format": "int64",
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "An id of a text auto reply"
      },
      "fields": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Limit fields received in response. E.g. fields: id, name or fields items (id, name), see more at [partial response](https://developers.callfire.com/docs.html#partial-response) page."
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "id"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "https://api.callfire.com/v2/texts/auto-replys/{id}{?fields}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Object"
        },
        "CallFire allows you to set up auto reply messages for your numbers CallFire allows you to set up auto reply messages for your numbers and keywords. You can set a general auto reply for anyone who texts your number (keyword). Also you can include a text to match, so that the auto reply would be sent only to those recipients whose texts the matched text",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**id**: An id of a text auto reply",
            "**keyword**: Setup autoreply for a given keyword",
            "**match**: Text to match. If it is set then autoreply will be sent to a person who texted message with matched text. Case insensitive, if parameter is not specified then all texts will be matched",
            "**message**: A text message to return as an auto reply",
            "**number**: Setup autoreply for a given phone number, E.164 format (11-digit). Example: 12132000384"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
